##------------------------------------------------------------------------
##  Registration
##------------------------------------------------------------------------

@NODE Registration "Registration"
                             Registration

Registration at the moment is pretty easy. Simply send an e-mail stating
the Amiga model, RAM size, CPU and Scion Genealogist database size (that
is the number of individuals and number of families) and whether the 
browser is of any use to you to one of the e-mail addresses mentioned 
on the @{"problem/bugreport" LINK "Problem"} screen.
        
                       @{underlined "That's it."}
        
Not too much to be asked ???


Well, you might ask yourself "Why should I register?".

To be honest, this question is not easy to be answered in general. However,
try to answer a counter question from me "Why should you not register?". 
I am very willing to argue anything you might come up with. Simply send me
your argument and I'll try to fight it. 

And please include the data asked for above, if somehow possible ;-)


I am convinced. In case ScionBrowser ever goes commercial, there will be 
a bonus for those who registered. Whenever and whatever that might be.
@ENDNODE


