##------------------------------------------------------------------------
##  Installation
##------------------------------------------------------------------------

@NODE Installation "Installation"
                             Installation

Make sure you have Workbench 2.04 and Scion Genealogist installed
on your system. You will need it.

The ScionBrowser distribution consists of an archive named
@{bold "ScionBrowser.lha"}. The contents of this archive is supposed to
be unarchived into your Scion Genealogist main directory, i.e. the
directory with the Scion Genealogist main program @{bold "Scion"}. 
@{underlined "Assuming"} this directory to be @{bold "work:my/hierarchy/Scion/"} 
copy the ScionBrowser distribution archive into that directroy and 
unarchive the archive using the following commands in a CLI:

         cd work:my/hierarchy/Scion/
         lha x ScionBrowser.lha

and after succesful expansion

         delete ScionBrowser.lha
         
The following files will be put into your Scion main directory:

         ScionBrowser
         ScionBrowser.info
         Guides/English/ScionBrowser.guide
         Guides/English/ScionBrowser.guide.info
        
Done.

@ENDNODE


